definitions.definition: The Prussian language; see Old Prussian and New Prussian .

main_definition: The Prussian language; see Old Prussian and New Prussian .

definitions.definition: A native or inhabitant of the geographical region of Prussia.
A citizen of the German state of Prussia.
A member of or a person descended from the Baltic ethnic group which inhabited Prussia.
A member of or a person descended from the German ethnic group which settled in Prussia.
examples: The Junkers were the stereotypical Prussians .
